snippet.title: Freeway Fury: Alien Annihilation — Launch Trailer — Android / iOS
snippet.description:
Freeway Fury: Alien Annihilation is the ultimate version of the popular arcade-action game.

Get it on the App Store:
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/freeway-fury-annihilation/id1535669567

Get it on Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.vascof.FreewayFury


Made by Serius Games.
Website: http://www.seriusgames.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SeriusGames
